raw disk(ebs volume to linux)

1.Format disk
2.create filesystem after formatting
3. after creating fs mount the disk

lsblk
1.fdisk /dev/xvdf
2. press n and hit enter 4 times at last again press w (it will format).
3.press lblk see (formatting)
4.mkfs.ext4 /dev/xvdf1 (to create fs after formatting)
5.mkdir /datavol1
6.mount /dev/xvdf1 /datavol1/ (for mounting)
